佳 SSD</a>的综合指南。您需要查看该文章以获取有关如何升级 SSD 的分步指南。但如果你想让事情尽可能简单，最好的选择是带有内置散热器的 Gen4 M.2 NVME SSD。 <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAUw3krPhvLRh64slxm7YihORKbiYwdC9qNqyxGsFuMI3&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB08PHSVW7K%2Fref%3Dox_sc_act_title_1%3Fsmid%3DATVPDKIKX0DER%26th%3D1">WD Black 的 SN850</a>是更好的即插即用选项之一。它符合索尼列出的所有兼容性要求，而且价格也很合理。</p><h2>三星 T7 固态硬盘</h2><p><core-commerce id="1fabda9f9e0f415589380651c85d832b" data-type="product-list"></p><p>如果您不愿意打开 PS5 来安装新的 SSD，另一种选择是购买外置固态硬盘。请记住， <a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5wbGF5c3RhdGlvbi5jb20vZW4tY2Evc3VwcG9ydC9oYXJkd2FyZS9wczUtZXh0ZW5kZWQtc3RvcmFnZS8iLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6ImI0NWUwZGJhLTlmZjgtNDlkOC05ZDQ1LTlhNzE0ZTM1NDYzMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAeuvMVb0tDrkV6Maoxe-9yhXyvRioDmB2pzWHLcDkMp4&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.playstation.com%2Fen-ca%2Fsupport%2Fhardware%2Fps5-extended-storage%2F">您不能从外部驱动器玩 PS5</a>游戏。但是，从 SSD 复制一个比从 PlayStation Store 下载它花费的时间更少。我们最喜欢的便携式硬盘之一是<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMDg3NFlKUDkyP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLWU0LTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiJiNDVlMGRiYS05ZmY4LTQ5ZDgtOWQ0NS05YTcxNGUzNTQ2MzAifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAU7Be52VhKJTXIv2Paq07vkf